{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Document: dragstart event","mdn_url":"/ru/docs/Web/API/Document/dragstart_event","locale":"ru","native":"Русский","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">Событие dragstart вызывается, когда пользователь начинает перетаскивать выделенный элемент или текст.</div>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Bubbles</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Отменяемое</th>\n   <td>Да</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Действие по умолчанию</th>\n   <td>Инициирование операции перетаскивания</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Интерфейс</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DragEvent\"><code>DragEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Свойство обработчика события</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragstart_event\" title=\"ondragstart\"><code>ondragstart</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"примеры","title":"Примеры","isH3":false,"content":"<p>See the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drag_event\">drag event</a> for example code or this <a href=\"http://jsfiddle.net/zfnj5rv4/\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"external\">JSFiddle demo</a>.</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Примеры sample\" id=\"frame_примеры\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drag_event/_sample_.%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Спецификации","id":"спецификации","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/dnd.html#event-dnd-dragstart","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Document